Name: rand-convolve
Version: 1.0.5
Summary: Runs a multi-random-kernel convolution on an image.
Home-page: https://github.com/aceynk/random_convolution
Author: aceynk
License: MIT
Project-URL: Issues, https://github.com/aceynk/random_convolution/issues
